<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 14:07:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>埃隆·马斯克誓言将与加沙相关的推文的广告收入捐赠给以色列和巴勒斯坦的医院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-22/ty-article/elon-musk-vows-to-donate-revenue-from-gaza-related-posts-to-israeli-palestinian-hospitals/0000018b-f701-d7a8-a9cf-f76971c50000</link><description>在网上引发轩然大波并因同意反犹太主义推文而失去主要广告商后，这位备受争议的亿万富翁决定通过发送 X 的广告资金来资助以色列、加沙的医疗服务来纠正自己的最新丑闻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 13:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-22/ty-article/elon-musk-vows-to-donate-revenue-from-gaza-related-posts-to-israeli-palestinian-hospitals/0000018b-f701-d7a8-a9cf-f76971c50000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡，滚吧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/letters/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-be-gone/0000018b-f687-d5e1-a5bb-ffcfa4480000</link><description>以色列总理无视知识渊博、能干的顾问向他发出的警告。结果就是10月7日哈马斯发动的悲惨致命袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 13:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/letters/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-be-gone/0000018b-f687-d5e1-a5bb-ffcfa4480000</guid></item><item><title>医院组建团队治疗获释的以色列人质：有些人质是女性，而且没有讲阿拉伯语的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-form-teams-to-treat-freed-hostages-some-are-all-female-have-no-arabic-speakers/0000018b-f6e5-d7a8-a9cf-f6ed3e320000</link><description>根据卫生部的指示，所有将接收被带回以色列的妇女和儿童人质的六家医院都建立了包括儿科医生、妇科医生和法律医学专家在内的团队</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 13:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-form-teams-to-treat-freed-hostages-some-are-all-female-have-no-arabic-speakers/0000018b-f6e5-d7a8-a9cf-f6ed3e320000</guid></item><item><title>“伤人”：苏珊·萨兰登因亲巴勒斯坦言论引发反犹太主义骚动而被经纪公司解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/hurtful-susan-sarandon-dropped-by-talent-agency-after-pro-palestinian-rally-speech/0000018b-f6c4-d55f-a3ff-fed775c60000</link><description>联合人才经纪公司与这位女演员断绝了关系，称她的言论“伤害了经纪公司的员工”；萨兰登为自己的言论辩护，引发了反犹太主义指控，称“大多数人都不了解 10 月 7 日袭击之前发生的事情的背景”</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 12:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/hurtful-susan-sarandon-dropped-by-talent-agency-after-pro-palestinian-rally-speech/0000018b-f6c4-d55f-a3ff-fed775c60000</guid></item><item><title>为什么卡塔尔需要成为哈马斯的避风港</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-qatar-needs-to-be-a-safe-haven-for-hamas/0000018b-f61e-d558-a3eb-f71f593a0000</link><description>尽管国际社会批评卡塔尔接待哈马斯，但多哈在斡旋以色列与哈马斯停火和人质协议方面所发挥的作用表明，它如何接近并影响其盟友的敌人，这既是混乱的，也是必要的</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 12:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-qatar-needs-to-be-a-safe-haven-for-hamas/0000018b-f61e-d558-a3eb-f71f593a0000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易将为哈马斯领导人提供保险，卡塔尔是保单持有人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-will-serve-as-insurance-for-hamas-leaders-with-qatar-as-the-policyholders/0000018b-f66e-d558-a3eb-f76f68a30000</link><description>卡塔尔在加沙战争中发挥着重要而强大的作用，这将使这个海湾小酋长国在哈马斯的未来和冲突的结果中发挥巨大的作用。同时，卡塔尔是美国的战略合作伙伴，也是美国企业和机构的最大投资者之一</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 11:05:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-will-serve-as-insurance-for-hamas-leaders-with-qatar-as-the-policyholders/0000018b-f66e-d558-a3eb-f76f68a30000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人称以色列军队袭击西岸难民营造成六人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/palestinians-say-six-killed-from-israeli-army-strike-in-west-bank-refugee-camp/0000018b-f695-d57c-adcb-fff574910000</link><description>当地消息人士称，一架以色列国防军无人机袭击了一座住宅，造成六人死亡、三人受伤。两名伤者被送往医院，第三人被捕</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 10:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/palestinians-say-six-killed-from-israeli-army-strike-in-west-bank-refugee-camp/0000018b-f695-d57c-adcb-fff574910000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯-以色列人质、停火协议：我们所知道的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/hamas-israel-hostage-deal-everything-we-know/0000018b-f66f-d57c-adcb-ffef76cf0000</link><description>哪些以色列人质将被释放？加沙与哈马斯的停火将持续多久？真主党会在北方忍住吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 10:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/hamas-israel-hostage-deal-everything-we-know/0000018b-f66f-d57c-adcb-ffef76cf0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯摧毁了加沙，但从以色列释放巴勒斯坦囚犯将提高其公众支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-lays-in-ruin-releasing-palestinian-prisoners-will-boost-hamas-public-support/0000018b-f61a-d6b9-af8f-ffbe1eaa0000</link><description>伤痕累累的哈马斯已经在巴勒斯坦公众中赢得了分数，甚至在最终释放可能数千名囚犯以换取加沙剩余人质之前</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 09:56:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-lays-in-ruin-releasing-palestinian-prisoners-will-boost-hamas-public-support/0000018b-f61a-d6b9-af8f-ffbe1eaa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯人质协议中将释放哪些巴勒斯坦囚犯？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/who-are-the-palestinians-prisoners-to-be-released-in-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018b-f625-d558-a3eb-f72f2ab40000</link><description>在批准与哈马斯的人质协议后，以色列公布了待释放的巴勒斯坦囚犯的姓名。该名单包括 123 名 18 岁以下的未成年人。其中 5 人年龄为 14 岁，因投掷燃烧弹和纵火等罪名被监禁</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 09:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/who-are-the-palestinians-prisoners-to-be-released-in-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018b-f625-d558-a3eb-f72f2ab40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考古学家在黎凡特南部发现最早的战争证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/israeli-archaeologists-find-earliest-evidence-of-war-in-southern-levant/0000018b-f2d6-d558-a3eb-f7df10480000</link><description>大约 8,000 年前，今天的以色列工业化生产具有空气动力学效率的弹石并不是为了捕猎动物</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 06:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/israeli-archaeologists-find-earliest-evidence-of-war-in-southern-levant/0000018b-f2d6-d558-a3eb-f7df10480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员确认哈马斯将于周四上午 10 点开始停火；真主党表示将加入暂停</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-live/israeli-cabinet-okays-deal-for-release-of-50-hostages-held-by-hamas-temporary-cease-fire/0000018b-f52c-d117-abcf-f7ef5d450000</link><description>以色列与哈马斯的协议包括从加沙释放 50 名人质，以换取 150 名巴勒斯坦囚犯 ■ 以色列公布 300 名候选释放囚犯的名单，给予公众 24 小时上诉时间 ■ 犹太复国主义政党投票支持协议，表示“将推进目标” ■ 以色列国防军继续加沙地面行动，宣布两名士兵死亡 ■ 据当地医疗消息来源称，图尔卡雷姆有五人死亡 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生，236 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制下卫生部：加沙14,128人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 04:11:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-live/israeli-cabinet-okays-deal-for-release-of-50-hostages-held-by-hamas-temporary-cease-fire/0000018b-f52c-d117-abcf-f7ef5d450000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡无视所有警告和迫在眉睫的威胁。他对这场灾难负有主要责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-all-the-warnings-and-pushed-the-palestinians-into-confrontation/0000018b-f398-d117-abcf-f7ffdb040000</link><description>以色列总理没有处理他收到的明确警告，而是专注于摧毁民主，确立自己的最高统治者地位，并将资源转移到极端正统派和定居点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-all-the-warnings-and-pushed-the-palestinians-into-confrontation/0000018b-f398-d117-abcf-f7ffdb040000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-f51f-d558-a3eb-f71f707c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 03:46:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-f51f-d558-a3eb-f71f707c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯达成为期四天的休战协议并释放50名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-hamas-agree-deal-for-four-day-truce-release-of-50-hostages/0000018b-f4ce-d117-abcf-f7efb3ee0000</link><description>由卡塔尔和美国斡旋的协议还将允许每天有 300 辆救援卡车通过与埃及接壤的拉法过境点进入加沙</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 02:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-hamas-agree-deal-for-four-day-truce-release-of-50-hostages/0000018b-f4ce-d117-abcf-f7efb3ee0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡迫于公众压力接受了他已经拒绝的同一份协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-buckled-under-public-pressure-to-accept-the-same-deal-he-already-rejected/0000018b-f458-dcf8-a3db-f7fa8b7a0000</link><description>以色列总理的曲折是理所当然的，但这一次似乎改变了他的想法的是公众压力、他与人质家属的会面以及以色列国防军、辛贝特和摩萨德所采取的立场</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 00:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-buckled-under-public-pressure-to-accept-the-same-deal-he-already-rejected/0000018b-f458-dcf8-a3db-f7fa8b7a0000</guid></item><item><title>我们决不能让哈马斯的残暴野蛮行为毒害我们的灵魂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-must-not-let-hamas-murderous-barbarism-poison-our-souls/0000018b-f3c2-d117-abcf-f7ef7f620000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 23:07:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-must-not-let-hamas-murderous-barbarism-poison-our-souls/0000018b-f3c2-d117-abcf-f7ef7f620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡知道。内塔尼亚胡置若罔闻。内塔尼亚胡负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/netanyahu-knew-netanyahu-ignored-netanyahu-is-responsible/0000018b-f3bf-d117-abcf-f7ff45870000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 22:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/netanyahu-knew-netanyahu-ignored-netanyahu-is-responsible/0000018b-f3bf-d117-abcf-f7ff45870000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡看来，军事情报部门正在抓捕他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-netanyahus-mind-military-intelligence-was-out-to-get-him/0000018b-f32f-d117-abcf-f7ef28910000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 21:50:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-netanyahus-mind-military-intelligence-was-out-to-get-him/0000018b-f32f-d117-abcf-f7ef28910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列同意放慢加沙战斗以营救被扣为人质的妇女和儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-accepts-a-slowdown-in-gaza-combat-to-rescue-women-and-children-held-hostage/0000018b-f38e-d558-a3eb-f78ff86a0000</link><description>以色列政府预计将批准的协议与上周拒绝的协议类似。从那时起，甘茨和国防官员担心公众对人质家人日益增长的支持可能会影响战斗</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2023 21:44:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-accepts-a-slowdown-in-gaza-combat-to-rescue-women-and-children-held-hostage/0000018b-f38e-d558-a3eb-f78ff86a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>